 the Public Record Office.<br />\n<br />\nPrior to this word being introduced to the English-speaking world, saffron already existed in the English language. Crog also referred to the saffron colour, so that orange was also referred to as ġeolurēad (yellow-red) for reddish orange, or ġeolucrog (yellow-saffron) for yellowish orange."},{"pid":"1fd719581c08c3cf220cc923d15973310c77108e","tid":861213,"uid":135169,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T03:08:29.000Z","msg":"其實係眼鏡蛇發明眼鏡"},{"pid":"cd2e77373a8b4cf90ef8cf2adc4abf4df1b807ac","tid":861213,"uid":33643,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T03:11:32.000Z","msg":"吹風蛇、扁頭蛇、吹風鱉、飯鏟頭、蝙蝠蛇、琵琶蛇、飯匙頭、萬蛇、膨頸蛇、扁頸蛇、五毒蛇、白頸丫"},{"pid":"a5aa4fd747ec84ff66698fe7561ee4eaf4cb7fce","tid":861213,"uid":193893,"like":1,"dislike":70,"score":-69,"quote":{"pid":"94cb648a706a25d8e10e3a95887b20df73c5a48d","tid":861213,"uid":86745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-14T03:04:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2018/10/14/bX8NgT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2018%2F10%2F14%2FbX8NgT.png&h=f89c0602&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2018-10-15T03:21:47.000Z","msg":"樓上成班傻西，冇一個係回緊樓主<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n個笑話唔係未有眼鏡之前睇野矇查查咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44911657fd519261ca5d5c5b5d0ad489e0432c60","tid":861213,"uid":33643,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"quote":{"pid":"a5aa4fd747ec84ff66698fe7561ee4eaf4cb7fce","tid":861213,"uid":193893,"like":1,"dislike":70,"score":-69,"quote":{"pid":"94cb648a706a25d8e10e3a95887b20df73c5a48d","tid":861213,"uid":86745